tent_hash":"d21509bfbdd0434644f7c29dc67581581b124eb710a6b6158ca7ca4d3174c7a8","event_uuid":"69343af1-9793-4006-8229-c375fee60db0","position":{"commit_sha":"119c35cb962cd69a001c98c1102e726ea69fb014","position":"1784438677664046838-69343af1-9793-4006-8229-c375fee60db0"},"signature":"{\"payload\": \"\", \"payloadType\": \"application/vnd.rebar.authorship.v1+json\", \"signatures\": [{\"keyid\": \"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d\", \"sig\": \"\"}]}","signer_pubkey":"ssh-ed25519 AAAAC3NzaC1lZDI1NTE5AAAAIHe3p+OG3L79IIh99qRBEkAEXaU+VbeQcSfhIu4M2F8b rebar-bot joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com"},{"content_hash":"122a380f2fbbcf8319d6d8b900c42b14945adeaedabf38ad790ec550846d3c74","event_uuid":"539e6938-3251-4e44-aba3-14ee97eb32a5","position":{"commit_sha":"05ecfe304f1af3f41474fa0404aa97e249f34a14","position":"1784439130027392001-539e6938-3251-4e44-aba3-14ee97eb32a5"},"signature":"{\"payload\": \"\", \"payloadType\": \"application/vnd.rebar.authorship.v1+json\", \"signatures\": [{\"keyid\": \"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d\", \"sig\": \"\"}]}","signer_pubkey":"ssh-ed25519 AAAAC3NzaC1lZDI1NTE5AAAAIHe3p+OG3L79IIh99qRBEkAEXaU+VbeQcSfhIu4M2F8b rebar-bot joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com"}],"bridge_alerts":[],"claim_harness":"claude-code_2-1-215_agent","claim_remote_session":null,"claimed_session":"688874f2-3b03-42c3-a76d-b602d9e889b5","comments":[{"author":"Joe Oakhart","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","author_id":"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d","body":"Pushed to Gerrit as change 819 (https://rebar.solutions.navateam.com/c/rebar/+/819). Naming cleanup implemented: 12 name: rewrites to the locked Title-Case table, eval.yml->prompt-eval.yml + verify-identity.yaml->verify-identity.yml renames, deleted eval-plan-review-container.yml (da34 closed), references updated (rebar.toml, docs/identity.md, docs/adr/0049, eval_specs README), and added tests/unit/test_workflow_names.py pinning names+extension. Local gates green: 40 workflow-pinning tests, make lint (ruff+actionlint), docs-index gate, 65 doc tests, pre-commit (lint+typecheck). Awaiting LLM-Review +1 and Verified +1 before submit.","timestamp":1784439130027392001}],"created_at":1784437625703684001,"creation_channel":"cli","deps":[],"description":"## Why\nThe GitHub Actions UI lists workflows by their `name:` field. Several workflows carry lowercase, non-descriptive `name:` values (test, release, optionality, _optionality, external-integration, verify-identity, terraform-drift, mirror-guard, gerrit-verify) and two use the `.yaml` extension against the ecosystem-standard `.yml`, so the Actions tab is hard to scan and inconsistent. eval.yml has a filename/name mismatch (name: prompt-eval), and eval-plan-review-container.yml is closed-out scaffolding for story da34 (safe-peg-tuner, CLOSED).\n\n## What (naming cleanup ONLY; reusable-workflow refactor is a SEPARATE later change)\nAdopt the researched standard used by popular repos + GitHub docs: filenames lowercase-with-hyphens + .yml only; `name:` short Title Case; reusable workflows keep the leading-underscore marker.\n\n- Rewrite `name:` values to descriptive Title Case per the locked table (Gerrit Verified Gate; Release; Optional-Dependency Isolation (reusable)/(mirror); Test Suite (mirror); Verify Authorship Identity; Prompt Eval; Live External Integration; Mirror Guard; PR Lockdown; Terraform Drift; CodeQL SAST).\n- Rename files: eval.yml -> prompt-eval.yml; verify-identity.yaml -> verify-identity.yml.\n- Delete eval-plan-review-container.yml (da34 closed; opt-in non-blocking, not a required check).\n- Update references: src/rebar/llm/eval_specs/README.plan-review.md (eval->prompt-eval, drop container ref); tests/unit/test_verify_opcert_heldout.py + docs/identity.md + docs/adr/0049-opcert-asymmetric.md (.yaml->.yml on verify-identity).\n\n## Locked filenames (NOT renamed)\n- gerrit-verify.yaml — Gerrit g2p dispatches by filename substring (verify+gerrit); renaming breaks the Verified vote. Stays the sole .yaml (accepted exception).\n- release.yml — PyPI OIDC trusted-publisher subject matches the workflow filename.\n\n## Out of scope (GitHub-managed dynamic workflows, not files): duplicate CodeQL default-setup slot, Dependency Graph, Dependabot Updates, Copilot.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] Every workflow has a descriptive Title Case `name:` per the locked table.\n- [ ] eval.yml renamed to prompt-eval.yml; verify-identity.yaml renamed to verify-identity.yml; all in-repo references updated.\n- [ ] eval-plan-review-container.yml deleted; its README reference removed.\n- [ ] gerrit-verify.yaml and release.yml filenames unchanged.\n- [ ] make lint passes (actionlint over all workflows) and the workflow-pinning tests pass: test_ci_workflow_parity.py, test_external_canary.py, test_verify_opcert_heldout.py, test_ci_actionlint_scope.py.\n- [ ] Lands through Gerrit with LLM-Review +1 and Verified +1.","env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","file_impact":[{"path":".github/workflows/gerrit-verify.yaml","reason":"name: -> Gerrit Verified Gate"},{"path":".github/workflows/release.yml","reason":"name: -> Release"},{"path":".github/workflows/_optionality.yml","reason":"name: -> Optional-Dependency Isolation (reusable)"},{"path":".github/workflows/optionality.yml","reason":"name: -> Optional-Dependency Isolation (mirror)"},{"path":".github/workflows/test.yml","reason":"name: -> Test Suite (mirror)"},{"path":".github/workflows/mirror-guard.yml","reason":"name: -> Mirror Guard"},{"path":".github/workflows/lockdown.yml","reason":"name: -> PR Lockdown"},{"path":".github/workflows/terraform-drift.yml","reason":"name: -> Terraform Drift"},{"path":".github/workflows/codeql.yml","reason":"name: -> CodeQL SAST"},{"path":".github/workflows/external-integration.yml","reason":"name: -> Live External Integration"},{"path":".github/workflows/eval.yml","reason":"rename -> prompt-eval.yml + name: Prompt Eval"},{"path":".github/workflows/verify-identity.yaml","reason":"rename -> verify-identity.yml + name: Verify Authorship Identity"},{"path":".github/workflows/eval-plan-review-container.yml","reason":"delete (da34 closed scaffolding)"},{"path":"src/rebar/llm/eval_specs/README.plan-review.md","reason":"update eval->prompt-eval ref; drop container ref"},{"path":"tests/unit/test_verify_opcert_heldout.py","reason":"update verify-identity.yaml->.yml path constant"},{"path":"docs/identity.md","reason":"update verify-identity.yaml->.yml references"},{"path":"docs/adr/0049-opcert-asymmetric.md","reason":"update verify-identity.yaml->.yml reference"}],"keyring":[],"last_status_env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","managed_refs":[],"parent_id":null,"parent_status_uuid":"f54dd8a5-5f37-44c6-8d57-6cc426f42016","preconditions_summary":{"status":"pre-manifest"},"priority":2,"reverts":[],"status":"in_progress","tags":[],"ticket_id":"b550-b5fc-b2e4-4396","ticket_type":"task","title":"GitHub Actions workflow naming cleanup: descriptive name: fields + standardize conventions","verify_commands":[]},"source_event_uuids":["ffbf98fa-8047-4472-a2dc-8ee54782ac6e","d303204c-f885-40c0-9b69-61c66c4411ce","44c6ad97-6f54-457b-9815-ddb11b79af40","f54dd8a5-5f37-44c6-8d57-6cc426f42016","1b84b713-65b2-4b4f-8170-ab4690ab82e4","69343af1-9793-4006-8229-c375fee60db0","539e6938-3251-4e44-aba3-14ee97eb32a5"]},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"SNAPSHOT","timestamp":1784439130027392002,"uuid":"0a72310e-997e-425d-bed7-3eccea11e391"}